Package net.jadler.matchers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BodyRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching the request body as a string.
    HeaderRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching a request header.
    MethodRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching the request method.
    ParameterRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching a request parameter.
    PathRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching the request path.
    QueryStringRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching the request query string.
    RawBodyRequestMatcher
    A RequestMatcher used for matching the request body as an array of bytes.
    RequestMatcher<T>
    Convenient base class for all Jadler request matchers.
